Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:11.95,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong! That ain't even close!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:14.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?! \NI played it exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.00,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't any swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:19.08,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,If you play it without feelin' it, \Nit don't sound like no jazz to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:23.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, do you know the name of the \Ntune he was playing on the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:27.46,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Art Blakey and the Jazz \NMessengers' "Moanin'".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:16.44,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,My aunt's gone grocery shopping for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:18.36,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I've got one hour to make it or break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:28.87,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Dissonant chords... Syncopation \Nand a unique accent...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:39.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I understood the distinctive \Nfeatures of jazz in my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:42.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but reproducing them was proving \Nto be extremely difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:11.76,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This guy don't get jazz one bit! \NAnd he got no sense for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:15.91,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! No matter what it \Ntakes, I'm gonna show him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:45.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna master this as soon as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:48.02,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,and then perform it in \Nfront of him and Ri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.47,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You win...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:54.77,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, that was wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.80,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,As if...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:58.43,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well. Nishimi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:03.01,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,You sure look like you're in \Na good mood. Where ya goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.41,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.61,Main Dialog,Tokieda,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:16.97,Main Dialog,Tokieda,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:21.25,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:22.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What'd I ever do to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:25.12,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's my neck, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:31.25,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,These days, I got a crick in \Nmy neck that just won't quit,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.86,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,an' it's puttin' me in the worst mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:36.25,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought havin' a little fun \Nlike this would brighten my day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:38.00,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Other than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:40.64,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,...you've kind of been gettin' \Non my nerves, recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:44.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:50.11,Main Dialog,Boy B,0000,0000,0000,,He's in the kendo team, \Nso you'd best not resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.17,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.23,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,There's trouble! Come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:01.99,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... How can we entertain ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.23,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,How about splitting a watermelon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:08.03,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,We can do better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.95,Main Dialog,Boy C,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we pants 'im?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.44,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.72,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:16.67,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move. Keep nice an' quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:19.92,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Students from the girls' school \Ncome home this way too,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:22.13,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,so this'll give them a good show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:36.00,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Too much momentum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.00,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:42.03,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when this jerk wakes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:45.24,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,tell 'im that no real man \Ngangs up on a weakling...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...? It's you, Richie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:52.74,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay, Yamaoka-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.96,Main Dialog,Boy C,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your front tooth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:57.83,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,What are you just standing there for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:01.34,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how you do it, \NI want him eatin' dirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:05.25,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:08.68,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,We gonna play a game, like \N"monkey in the middle"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:11.97,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:17.08,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ri-chan! What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:19.81,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro will take care of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.66,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,so get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:27.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Clearly, you boys \Nain't used to scrappin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:31.08,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I look pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:34.91,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan literally caught \Nme with my pants down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:37.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that, she rescued me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:43.99,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, would you hold \Non to my glasses for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.58,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:02.36,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll pay you back for \Nknocking out my front tooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:12.14,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:15.23,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:19.71,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Little twerp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.45,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Get 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.48,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.68,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's startin' to get interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:37.70,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.78,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well? You up for some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:53.66,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm gonna see to it that everyone \Nin class gives you the cold shoulder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:56.87,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You an' me are in the same class?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:59.62,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Can't remember seein' this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.63,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,B-Be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.52,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My neck feels better...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:09.10,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, your forehead is \Nbleeding... Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:10.88,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry 'bout his forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:13.99,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Those fingers of yours doin' okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:20.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. He's actually keeping \Nan eye out for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:24.83,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:27.47,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you took another good pounding, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:29.53,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:30.99,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Go on downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:33.17,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be Brother Jun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:35.99,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:40.64,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the squirt beat up, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.20,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He was in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:44.43,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:45.31,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:49.47,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sen-boy, you been gettin' rowdy again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:52.80,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, today\N wasn't much of a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:55.17,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's good to see \Nyou're in fighting form.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:57.35,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,So who's this cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:08:59.77,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,He's my buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.77,0:09:03.39,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. Cool. An odd couple, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.00,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:07.25,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we're not friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:14.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:19.91,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Say, is he your brother, Ri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:24.05,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh. Brother Jun is from next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:26.71,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Now he's a university student in Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:27.54,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.53,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Mind the store for just one tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:35.28,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, you always say "just one tune", but \Nthen you don't come up for two hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:38.15,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's not every day that Junichi \Ncomes back to town... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:41.35,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, I'm asking you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:45.06,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I'll treat you \Nto a cream soda at our shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:47.82,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,How about throwing in a cream puff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:49.03,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Natch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:52.89,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We got us a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:53.57,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:56.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,G-Get what started?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:10.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,A live session...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:23.52,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, get over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:24.58,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:26.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:29.48,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Just make some noise, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:44.65,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so jittery for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:46.87,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat the details, just jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:45.21,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? So you've been playing \Njazz for just two weeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:50.37,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing. It was all over \Nthe place, but you got the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.20,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You've played piano for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:53.98,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:57.99,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,How about coming over \Nhere from now on to practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:01.27,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,He'll come every day even \Nwithout being told, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:06.45,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have to get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.31,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:10.61,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right, Brother Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.68,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's the name of that record \Nyou were gonna tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:16.01,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the Elvin Jones one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:18.19,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it. "Tommy" something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:20.84,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,"Flanagan". Maybe it's upstairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:22.94,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us are alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:27.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:32.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, what do you usually \Ndo on your days off?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:34.78,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean with summer vacation coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:40.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right. I was thinking maybe \Nwe could do our homework together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:44.70,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! I bet I could make real progress \Nworking on it with you, Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:47.08,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,How's next Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:49.19,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Would 11 work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:50.67,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:53.93,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Let's meet up \Nthere, behind the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.32,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, I'll draw you a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:03.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... Summer vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:08.04,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, all my summer vacations \Nhave been spent alone in my room,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:10.62,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,with far too much time on my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:15.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? I have so \Nmany things to look forward to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:17.28,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,that I can't wrap my head around it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'm a little early...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:38.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Church on Sunday morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:52.06,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:55.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...is a Christian?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:05.32,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Him too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:18.72,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.66,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:22.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. Well, should we...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:23.17,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:25.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This is how we're going to the library?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:40.74,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, why is he with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:48.70,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Kanoko-mae Wharf\NBus Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:50.55,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um... What about the library?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:53.70,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot today. Doesn't it \Nfeel much better at the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:56.21,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro agreed this was the way to go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:15:01.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan... I meant for this to be a date...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:05.21,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I rented a boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:06.93,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hop in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:14.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,How did it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.65,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd it end up the three of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.15,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, give me a bite of that, wouldya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:25.11,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the face?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.86,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't the rower get any kind \Nof reward for his services?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:29.29,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro, you can finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:31.16,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, he can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.32,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:36.86,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh... Fine! Here, eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:42.36,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,One bite, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:54.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, do you always have a cross on, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:57.08,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I have a rosary,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:16:00.13,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not something you're \Nsupposed to wear around your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:03.22,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Our priest says Sentaro is special, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:04.02,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:06.55,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell him all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:12.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,For just a second there, the tension \Nwas thick enough to cut with a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Or was it just in my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:18.17,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:22.88,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, aren't you going to swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:27.38,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,We came all this way, so let's take a dip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:32.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, I didn't \Nbring along a bathing suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:36.84,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Neither did Sentaro. He's \Njust wearing his undies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:40.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's swim, Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.06,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:46.44,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ri'ko, hurry up and dive in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:48.24,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:52.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you bein' bashful about? \NYou're flat as a washboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:57.00,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Last time we went swimmin', you \Nhad nothin' but your slip on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:17:00.60,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, for goodness sake! That's when \Nwe were in elementary school!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:04.44,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say weird things like \Nthat in front of Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:05.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:06.39,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:08.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:10.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko, pinch your nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.22,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:16.37,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alley-oop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:19.56,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:20.71,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:21.93,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:28.82,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, for...! You're an ogre, Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:33.07,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It feels good, don't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:35.96,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He really is a jerk, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:42.58,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Kaoru-san... Why do you \Nkeep swimming in circles?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:47.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only way I know how to \Nswim with my head out of the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:50.96,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, you're a funny guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:53.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,She laughed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:58.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I feel so happy when this girl smiles?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:07.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I feel like I could do \Nanything for that smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:14.74,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two look like you're \Nhavin' fun. Let me join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:18.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! Ri-chan, let's get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.37,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:22.75,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:24.51,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you swimmin' away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:33.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I only wish that we could keep going...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That I could take you away from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:01.57,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's trade places.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:05.04,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take over the rowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:07.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty hard, y'know. \NAnd on top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:08.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:13.79,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.74,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna switch, Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:18.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not about strength, \Nbut how you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:21.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,And I think I'm getting the hang of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:23.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I'm complainin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:26.48,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,...but you've been takin' us in circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:34.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Cool. You took us to a \Ncompletely different beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:37.31,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:39.11,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The sun is already setting anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:42.00,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,so if we tell the boat rental guy what \Nhappened, he'll come by and pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:49.62,Main Dialog,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, girl, have a little fun with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:52.74,Main Dialog,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so stuck-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:54.63,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,No! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.39,Main Dialog,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't gonna hurt ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:57.58,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:20:00.82,Main Dialog,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,We got a car, so let us take you for a ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:02.52,Main Dialog,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:05.22,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. The lady ain't willin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.06,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,So how about gettin' your mitts off her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:09.63,Main Dialog,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?! Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:14.15,Main Dialog,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,Actin' so tough... What, are \Nyou tryin' to be a hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:18.05,Main Dialog,Man 3,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this dude is Kawabuchi from East High!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:21.12,Main Dialog,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,East High... You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:23.20,Main Dialog,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,Kawabuchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:33.21,Main Dialog,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This time, I'll let you off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:39.01,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.45,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:21:01.29,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It happened in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:06.96,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize what \Nhad just taken place...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.38,0:21:13.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...but when it comes to falling in \Nlove, you don't need a reason or time.
